::Rex::

Rex raises an eyebrow as Battera walks back into the base. He shakes his 
head. He could never understand femms. One second, Battera was nearly getting 
herself scrapped to go outside, the next she was heading back to her room.

He silently follows her to make sure she goes into her room, and doesn't 
wander around the ship.
